---
title: Teriyaki Beef, Tofu & Garlic Rice with Veggies & Crispy Shallots
description: This teriyaki tofu is drawing us in, sweet and savoury beef and far too hard to resist! Go ahead and give in, fill up your bowls with rice, stir-fried veggies and, of course, the all important teriyaki tofu. Pile it high and dig in!

*We’ve replaced the broccoli in this recipe with asparagus due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
